<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta name="csrf-token" content="<%= csrfToken %>">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <script src="/js/session-management-module.js" defer></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div
        class="container mt-5 mb-5"
        id="session-management-module-root"
        data-session-management-overview-endpoint="/api/session-management/overview"
        data-session-management-evaluate-endpoint="/api/session-management/evaluate">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4 flex-wrap gap-3">
            <div>
                <h1 class="notes-title mb-1">Session Management Module</h1>
                <p class="text-muted mb-2">A research workspace for strict session timeout policy, abandoned-terminal lockout, and concurrent-login prevention.</p>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Inspect the live session state, review the timeout policy in force for the current network zone, and simulate whether an abandoned or superseded session should be locked immediately.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <a href="/research" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Back to Research</a>
                <a href="/mission-assurance/module" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Open Mission Assurance Module</a>
                <a href="/hardware-mfa/module" class="btn btn-outline-dark">Open Hardware-First MFA Module</a>
                <a href="/notes" class="btn btn-secondary">Back to Notes</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Session State</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1" id="session-management-state-badge">Loading</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Current server-side session verdict.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Idle Timeout</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1" id="session-management-idle-timeout">0m</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Maximum inactivity before the session locks.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Absolute Lifetime</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1" id="session-management-absolute-timeout">0h</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Maximum total session lifetime before re-authentication.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-xl-3">
                <div class="card research-summary-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="research-kicker mb-2">Single Session</p>
                        <p class="display-6 mb-1 fs-3" id="session-management-concurrent-badge">Loading</p>
                        <p class="text-muted mb-0">Whether a newer login revokes the older one.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card automation-card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column flex-xl-row justify-content-between align-items-xl-center gap-3">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="h5 mb-1">Session Control Posture</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted mb-1">The session layer should enforce inactivity lockouts, maximum session lifetimes, and server-side invalidation when the same account signs in elsewhere.</p>
                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0" id="session-management-status-copy">Loading current session posture...</p>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
                    <button type="button" id="session-management-refresh-btn" class="btn btn-outline-secondary">Refresh Module</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body pt-0">
                <div id="session-management-status"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4 mb-4">
            <div class="col-xl-5">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Current Session</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Live Session State</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">This is the server-side session state currently bound to the authenticated browser.</p>
                        <div id="session-management-summary"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-7">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Controls</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Session Security Controls</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">These controls are the backbone of abandoned-terminal lockout and single-session enforcement.</p>
                        <div id="session-management-controls" class="row g-3"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Simulation</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Evaluate Lockdown Scenarios</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">Simulate a field-abandonment or concurrent-login event and confirm whether the session should stay alive or lock immediately.</p>
                        <form id="session-management-form" class="row g-3">
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <label for="session-management-scenario-select" class="form-label">Scenario</label>
                                <select id="session-management-scenario-select" class="form-select">
                                    <option value="">Loading scenarios...</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <label for="session-management-network-zone" class="form-label">Network Zone</label>
                                <select id="session-management-network-zone" class="form-select">
                                    <option value="corp">Corp</option>
                                    <option value="mission">Mission</option>
                                    <option value="public">Public</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <label for="session-management-idle-minutes" class="form-label">Idle Minutes</label>
                                <input type="number" min="0" step="1" class="form-control" id="session-management-idle-minutes" value="0">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-md-4">
                                <label for="session-management-elapsed-hours" class="form-label">Elapsed Hours</label>
                                <input type="number" min="0" step="0.5" class="form-control" id="session-management-elapsed-hours" value="0">
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <div class="form-check">
                                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" value="1" id="session-management-concurrent-toggle">
                                    <label class="form-check-label" for="session-management-concurrent-toggle">
                                        Simulate a newer login for the same account
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-12">
                                <button type="button" id="session-management-evaluate-btn" class="btn btn-dark">Evaluate Scenario</button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xl-6">
                <div class="card automation-card h-100">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <span class="research-kicker">Decision</span>
                        <h2 class="h4 mt-2 mb-1">Lockdown Decision</h2>
                        <p class="text-muted small mb-3">The result explains whether the session survives or gets locked, and which control forced that outcome.</p>
                        <div id="session-management-evaluation"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
